{
  "stem": "26792.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he remained, and wanted to wait a couple of years until he'll make some money in order to join her.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Unfortunately, he failed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And here we come to '41, June, '41, and your parents come to join you with your sister to Riga.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Where do they live?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Where do you live, all of them?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We all live in that small room which I mentioned before.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, everything was very sad, because the time had begun when Jewish people could not get any food.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It means-- if Latvians saw a Jew, or a Jew was standing, queuing up for food, they were just dragged away.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But since I looked in my early-- in my young days-- non-Jewish, and spoke the language very well, so I made the purchases for all the family and even for the neighbors, because in our house, there were some neighbors who were later killed, too.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no work at all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Jewish people were not supposed to work-- only forced labor given by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I tried, as much as I could, to defend my family in all respects.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My family means my parents and my little sister.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Since I was the older one and rather energetic, and I had got used to being on my own, I decided to go out into the street in the first place-- which was very dangerous on the first of July, when the Russian troops occupied the city-- Jewish people were hiding, and I wanted to see what was going on.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wouldn't do it today.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I saw Latvian women throwing flowers at the occupying German forces, singing songs, being dressed in their national dresses.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a great festivity in the country.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
